title: [WEEX-525] Created the automate beta branch-off scripts.
body:
The script beta-branchoff.sh is to automate the weekly beta release
branch-off procedure. It helps to identify which is the latest
non-RC version number and release a new beta branch with the number.
The branch will be branched-off from origin/master and will be pushed
onto apache after its creation.

A valid beta version number looks like: 0.18.0-beta1
A Valid beta branch name looks like: 0.18.0-beta1-180720

common.sh provides some useful gadgets for the scripts and can be
shared across scripts.

Apple announced deprecation of libstdc++ about 5 years ago.

Support for it was removed from the iOS 12.0 Simulator runtime, but it remains in the iOS 12.0 (device) runtime for binary compatibility with shipping apps.

see: https://twitter.com/jeremyhu/status/1003882060556062720

title: * [jsfm] using rollup.watch to fix dev build
body:
The `rollup-watch` package is deprecated and it will cause error:
```
$ npm run dev:jsfm
(node:40511) UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning: TypeError: Cannotread property 'map' of undefined
```
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8298849/42163619-e33a3cbc-7e35-11e8-8042-39a9c4079126.png)

Using `rollup.watch` to fix this issue.
